(48, 1, '2018-09-24 13:04:39', '2018-09-24 13:04:39', '<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-49 alignleft\" src=\"http://localhost/co/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/navin-239x300.jpg\" alt=\"navin kapoor\" width=\"239\" height=\"300\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">On 9th August 2018, NIIT University lost one of the most respected personality, Dr. Navin Kapur, Professor of Electronics &amp; Communications Engineering due to a cardiac arrest. His love for the students had drawn him to NIIT University. In this tragic moment, NU stands together in offering heartfelt condolences to his family. By his friendly and humble nature and his ever-smiling face, Professor Navin Kapur had captured everyone’s heart in his brief period with NU. This loss is irreplaceable and his memories shall always remain with us.\" title=\"OBITUARY - Demise of Prof.Navin Kapur</p>', 'Demise of Prof.Navin Kapur', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'demise-of-prof-navin-kapur__trashed', '', '', '2018-11-09 10:51:32', '2018-11-09 10:51:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost/co/?p=48', 0, 'post', '', 0),
