(245, 1, '2018-11-09 10:55:10', '2018-11-09 10:55:10', '<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-246 alignleft\" src=\"http://localhost/co/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/nu1-300x142.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"142\" />A workshop on the topic ‘Learning to Solve Problems– An Exploration’ was organised for the batch of 2022 during Resonance at NIIT University. The aim of the workshop was to make students understand the applications of learning imbibed through engineering education in the real environment. While the technical education will train the mind, it is the application part which acts as a key to solve the problems, especially in scenarios where Google may not be able to find you the solutions. The workshop helped the students in providing insights into how to fathom real life problems in an effective way and how to empathise with people. The workshop provided an impetus to the newbies to start-off their journey with confidence and focus.', '\'Learning to solve problem’ Workshop in Resonance', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'learning-to-solve-problem-workshop-in-resonance', '', '', '2018-11-15 17:20:00', '2018-11-15 17:20:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/co/?p=245', 0, 'post', '', 0),
