(287, 1, '2018-11-09 12:00:48', '2018-11-09 12:00:48', '<strong><em>Mr. Arun Maira</em></strong> was invited on 3<sup>rd</sup> August 2018 for a talk at NU campus. He is a management consultant and <strong><em>former member of</em></strong> <strong><em>Planning Commission of India</em></strong>. He is also <strong><em>former</em></strong> <strong><em>India Chairman of Boston Consulting Group</em></strong>. Mr. Maira emphasized on the importance of listening and the difference between hearing, listening and their correlation with understanding. The thoughtful session ended with an interactive discussion with the students.<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-285\" src=\"http://localhost/co/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-286\" src=\"http://localhost/co/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/nu1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"567\" />', 'Talk by Mr. Arun Maira', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '284-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-09 12:00:48', '2018-11-09 12:00:48', '', 284, 'http://localhost/co/284-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
