(295, 1, '2018-11-09 12:07:15', '2018-11-09 12:07:15', 'Techniche, the biggest and most exciting tech fests in India, was held from 30<sup>th</sup>August - 3<sup>rd</sup>September 2018 at IIT Guwahati. NUtons along with the Robotics club of NIIT University showcased their immense talent and bagged a number of prizes in the fest which included 3<sup>rd</sup> place in Emulate (Electronics and Electrical Event), Mechanema (Mechanical Designing Event) and Madmax (Bluetooth controlled and wired bots for shooting and defending in an arena) and 4<sup>th </sup>place in Robowars.<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-296\" src=\"http://localhost/co/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/17.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-297\" src=\"http://localhost/co/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/17-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"842\" height=\"1275\" />', 'Techniche IIT Guwahati 2018', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'techniche-iit-guwahati-2018', '', '', '2018-11-09 12:07:55', '2018-11-09 12:07:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/co/?p=295', 0, 'post', '', 0),
