(299, 1, '2018-11-09 12:10:21', '2018-11-09 12:10:21', 'Sai Yeshwanth B. Tech (2015-2019), presented a research paper on ‘Prediction based Smart Farming’ in IC2IE 2018 on 12-13<sup>th</sup> September 2018 in Indonesia. The paper was prepared under the guidance of Prof. Jitendra Joshi in collaboration with the group members which included Prajwal Brijesh Ainapur, Mayank Singh and Sangamesh Kotalwar. They recieved the ‘Best Paper Award’ and the award for ‘Best Presenter’ and the paper will now beExpr published in IOP science. This paper has also been selected for publishing in journal with some extended content.<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-300\" src=\"http://localhost/co/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/18.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"642\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-301\" src=\"http://localhost/co/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/19.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"513\" height=\"483\" />', 'Research Paper Presentation at Indonesia', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'research-paper-presentation-at-indonesia', '', '', '2018-11-09 12:10:21', '2018-11-09 12:10:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/co/?p=299', 0, 'post', '', 0),
